## Performance Instrumentation

```rust
use std::time::Instant;

let start = Instant::now();
let result = operation()?;
tracing::debug!(
    operation = "fts_search",
    query = %query,
    results = result.len(),
    duration_ms = start.elapsed().as_millis(),
    "Search completed"
);
```

Use structured fields (`key = value`) rather than format strings so logs are
machine-parseable. The `%` sigil calls `Display`; `?` calls `Debug`.